data.description: This well built all-brick, four-level detached single-family home is sure to captivate you with a timeless charm that is exuded in every corner of this traditional American Dream Home.   Step inside and be welcomed by the warm and inviting atmosphere, enhanced by the stunning hardwood floors that sprawl throughout the home. The rich, natural tones create an aura of comfort and sophistication, setting the stage for an upgraded traditional living experience.  The main level offers an inviting formal living space, perfect for hosting gatherings or simply relaxing after a long day. The adjacent formal dining area is perfect for elevating every meal into an elegant dining experience. The classic kitchen is truly the heart of this home, it is adorned with timeless finishes and an attached sunroom perfect for breakfast coffee or evening tea.   One of the standout features of this home is its four-level floor plan. Stretching over multiple levels, it provides a sense of privacy and exclusivity for every family member. The conventional family room offers intimacy and elegance with a real wood-burning brick fireplace that adds function along with a touch of nostalgia that creates an ambiance perfect for family gatherings or a quiet night with special friends.   Besides its charming interior, this home sits on a half-acre lot in the HOA-free neighborhood of Sherwood Forest. Don't miss the chance to make this stunning home your own.
